There are such plans.
We are conducting active negotiations with the Libyans, several delegations from Libya have already visited Moscow, and announced their readiness to come back to Moscow or Grozny.
And when can such negotiations take place?
Now it is hard to say.
Several visits should still take place, and then I hope that there will be clarity about the time and place of negotiations.
